HELP1_1: You need achieve the maximum rating and the high status by increasing well-being.
HELP2_1: Almost every event in this game is happened due to selection of random numbers.
HELP2_2: Every move in this game is equal to one day. Every day, you lose health, happiness and satiety in accordance with the random number.
HELP2_3: Health is increased by tablets, treatment, or sports.
HELP2_4: The satiety increases by food, visit the café or via marriage.
HELP2_5: Happiness increases with alcohol or sport.
HELP2_6: If your health, satiety, mood, or the money will drop by zero you will have only 7 days for improving. Otherwise you will die.
HELP2_7: Every year you will celebrate your Birthday and get presents.
HELP2_8: Every day you have a chance to find bottles in the trash bin and sell them.
THE_GAME_HAS_THE_PLAYER_STATUS_WHICH_ARE: The game has the player status, which are assigned for the achievements
HELP4_1: You can use currency exchange only after arithmetics learning.
HELP4_3: Periodically there are news about the increase or decrease rate. This will help to make more money on the difference in exchange rates.
HELP4_4: Price per bottle varies from 1 to 10 money randomly.
HELP4_5: Rate of exchange and price per bottle will be changed every move in this game.
HELP5_1: More expensive food and drinks will be more profitable for you.
HELP5_2: Food from trash bin will drop your health, happiness and rating randomly from 0% to 4%.
HELP5_3: Marriage gives the satiety between 20% and 40% daily.
HELP5_4: A drink in the bar gives happiness between 15% and 25% daily.
HELP6_1: The farther you move away from the suburbs towards the city center, the higher the probability to get the money. But at the same time increases the probability of losing more health and mood.
HELP6_2: Begging have also random nature of profit, but to use you need material and certain rating.
HELP7_1: You can work as a cleaner or a cars washer only after school ending. Also you need buy a tent.
HELP7_2: You can work as a plumber or factory operator after graduating from college.. Also you have to rent a room.
HELP7_3: You can work at the office after graduating from college. You also need to rent apartments.
HELP7_4: You can only be a manager after graduating abroad. You also have to buy your own apartment.
HELP7_5: You can earn money on the stock exchange only after graduation abroad. Also you must have your own office.
HELP7_6: Frauds on the stock exchange are punishable.
HELP7_7: You must become a deputy to meet in the government.
HELP7_8: You have to become the Minister of Defence to sell arms.
HELP7_9: You have to become the Minister of Finance to allocate the budget.
HELP7_10: You need to become a president to run the country.
HELP8_1: The more expensive health will be more useful for you.
HELP8_2: Jogging adds free health, but it can be a cause of reduction of satiety or happiness.
HELP8_3: Fitness Club provides health from 5% to 10% daily.
HELP8_4: Personal trainer gives health between 10% and 20% daily.
HELP8_5: You know when your character will die with  "Visit a fortune."
HELP8_6: Immortality pill allows the character to live forever.
HELP9_1: You can study in school only after sport shoes buying and arithmetics learning.
HELP9_2: You can study in college only after bike buying and school ending.
HELP9_3: You can study in bachelor’s degree only after cheap car's purchase and college ending.
HELP9_4: You can study abroad only after sport car's purchase and bachelor’s degree finishing.
HELP10_1: You will get a random bottle from 0 to 10 a day, becoming a senior homeless. But you have to be careful. Buy an amulet or hire a bodyguard.
HELP10_2: Creating a social network - a profitable business. But you better to hire a lawyer.
HELP10_3: The amulet reduces the possibility of negative events by half.
HELP10_5: A lawyer helps reduce losses of legal troubles.
HELP11_1: If your rating is more than 2,000,000, you can become a deputy or Minister.
HELP11_2: If you become a deputy or minister, it increases your chance of becoming president.
HELP11_3: If your status is not below the boss, you can run for president.
HELP11_4: If your rating above 2000, you can get a ID card.
HELP11_5: Unemployment benefit amounts to 100 money daily. It is paid as long as you are not working. ID card is required.
HELP11_6: Disability benefits amounts to 100 money daily. As long as it is paid, your health does not exceed 50%. ID card is required.
HELP11_7: You can receive a pension after 60 years. The amount of pension depends on the status. ID card is required.
